@startuml
!theme plain
title 04. RDMA and GPU-Direct Paths
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Coherence-CE" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "RoCEv2 fabric" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "GPU direct path" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "DPU/NIC" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Remote storage/object" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : hydration
N2 --> N3 : RDMA read/write
N3 --> N4 : direct DMA
N4 --> N5 : offload

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
